These are some of the tags that we support inside a text element

<A href="URL"></A>
	Anchor. The enclosed text is treated as a link to another entry named by URL.
	The text inside the tags is displayed using the "Link" text format.

<BR>
	Paragraph break.

<I></I>
	Emphasis. The text inside these tags is displayed using the "Emphasis" text format.

<EVAL>(add 2 2)</EVAL>

The following URL formats are supported:

core://all						-> a list of all documents
core://categories				-> a list of all categories
core://category/xxxxx			-> a list of all documents of category xxxxx
core://entry/nnnnn				-> where nnnnn is an UNID
